sourcesContent:
import styled from 'styled-components';

const InputContainer = styled.div`
	padding: 0.8rem 0;
	display: flex;
	gap: 1rem;
`;

const Label = styled.label`
	font-size: 1rem;
	display: block;
	padding-left: 15px;
`;

const Input = styled.input`
	width: 25px;
	height: 15px;
	padding: 0;
	margin: 0;
	vertical-align: bottom;
	position: relative;
`;

const StyledForm = styled.form`
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: center;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	background-color: white;
	width: 100%;
`;

const CheckboxContainer = styled.div`
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	width: 20%;
`;

const InputGroup = styled.div`
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(50px, 5rem));
	gap: 2rem;
`;

const CheckboxItem = styled.div`
	display: flex;
`;

function RecipeFilter() {
	return (
		<StyledForm>
			<CheckboxContainer>
				<Label> Intolerances </Label>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Dairy</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Gluten</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Peanut</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Sesame</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Seafood</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Shellfish</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Nuts</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Wheat</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>
			</CheckboxContainer>

			<CheckboxContainer>
				<Label> Diets </Label>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>GlutenFree</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Ketogenic </Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Vegetarian </Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>LactoVegetarian </Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>OvoVegetarian </Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Vegan</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Pescatarian</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Paleo</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Primal</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>LowFODMAP</Label>
				</CheckboxItem>

				<CheckboxItem>
					<Input type='checkbox' />
					<Label>Whole30 </Label>
				</CheckboxItem>
			</CheckboxContainer>

			<InputGroup>
				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCal'> Min Calories </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCal'> Max Calories </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCarbs'> Min Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCarbs'> Max Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minProtein'> Min Protein </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxProtein'> Max Protein </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSugar'> Min Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSugar'> Max Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSodium'> Min Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSodium'> Max Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSatFat'> Min Saturated Fat </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSatFat'> Max Saturated Fat</Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>
			</InputGroup>
		</StyledForm>
	);
}

export default RecipeFilter;
